.TH "amdgpu_device_ip_wait_for_idle" 9 "amdgpu_device_ip_wait_for_idle" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
amdgpu_device_ip_wait_for_idle \- wait for idle
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" amdgpu_device_ip_wait_for_idle
.BI "(struct amdgpu_device *adev "  ","
.BI "enum amd_ip_block_type block_type "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "adev" 12
amdgpu_device pointer
.IP "block_type" 12
Type of hardware IP (SMU, GFX, UVD, etc.)
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Waits for the request hardware IP to be idle.
Returns 0 for success or a negative error code on failure.
